channel.title: 317 - Thieving Stalls, EXP rates
channel.description: How do I change the item, and the amount of am item from a thieving stall on a 317 source. Also how do I change the exp rates for combat skills and skiller skills. Thanks!

item.title: 317 - Thieving Stalls, EXP rates
item.dc:creator: @X_Entinity_X X Entinity X
item.description:
@X_Entinity_X wrote:

Are you useing Delta or Project Insanity, if your useing Delta go into client.java and search “recieve”, then change the ammount ( the number, say for instance, if you thieve 5k, change it to whatever number) and the last number something like this: 80* or whatever, change it to whatever you want.

For Project Insanity, go into ActionHandler.Java and search the stall id, then change the first name (id of the item) to 995, then change the second number to how much you want from the stall.

Hope this helped.
